PN,31301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,FWith recorded violence and
OL,8,Fintimidation against women and girls
OL,9,Frising by nearly 18% in one year
OL,10,Facross Britain's transport network,
OL,11,FITV News Correspondent Stacey Foster
OL,12,Fjoined a police taskforce set stopping
OL,13,Fsexual offenders - but will their
OL,14,Fstrategy make women safer?
OL,16,FI met Esme just 10 days after she had
OL,17,Fbeen sexually assaulted while
OL,18,Ftravelling home on a train.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,FShe had recently shared a video on
OL,8,FTikTok describing what had happened.
OL,9,FThousands of people watched it and
OL,10,Fhundreds contacted her to share their
OL,11,Fown experiences.
OL,13,FAs we spoke about the impact the
OL,14,Fassault had had on her, she told me it
OL,15,Fwas the second time she had reported a
OL,16,Fsexual offence to British Transport
OL,17,FPolice using its 61016 text service.
OL,19,FThe first happened in March 2024 on a
OL,20,FJubilee line train near Canning Town.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,F"It was standing room only," she told
OL,8,Fme. "I looked down and there was a man
OL,9,Fmasturbating on me."
OL,11,FDespite CCTV appeals, nobody has ever
OL,12,Fbeen identified.
OL,14,FBritish Transport Police told ITV News
OL,15,Fthat while its investigation into the
OL,16,FJune 2026 assault remains ongoing, the
OL,17,F2024 investigation was closed after
OL,18,F"all lines of enquiry were exhausted",
OL,19,Fpending any new information.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,FEsme admits that has shaken her
OL,8,Fconfidence.
OL,10,F"They just have to wait and hope that
OL,11,Fmaybe these people might assault you
OL,12,Fagain. Or they might offend again, and
OL,13,Fthey'll catch them someplace else,"
OL,14,Fshe said.
OL,16,FTo understand what happens after
OL,17,Fsomeone sends that first text message,
OL,18,FITV News was given exclusive access to
OL,19,Fthe force's new Violence Against Women
OL,20,Fand Girls Taskforce.
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,FRecorded offences have risen by almost
OL,8,F18% over the past year. British
OL,9,FTransport Police believes that rise is
OL,10,Fbeing driven by more victims feeling
OL,11,Fable to report what has happened to
OL,12,Fthem.
OL,14,FI visit the contact centre in
OL,15,FBirmingham, where every text sent to
OL,16,F61016 is assessed by call handlers. In
OL,17,FJune alone, the team received 27,364
OL,18,Fmessages.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,FI spent an afternoon sitting beside
OL,8,FAJ, watching reports arrive in real
OL,9,Ftime.
OL,11,FOne message read: "I'm on a train from
OL,12,FPaddock Wood to Strood. There's two
OL,13,Fboys taking photos of me and recording
OL,14,Fvideos of me."
OL,16,FWithin seconds, AJ was identifying the
OL,17,Ftrain, locating the nearest station
OL,18,Fand creating an incident log for
OL,19,Fofficers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,FHis reply to the victim asked for
OL,8,Fdescriptions of the suspects and
OL,9,Fadvised the passenger to move
OL,10,Fsomewhere safe, if possible.
OL,12,FEverything happened remarkably
OL,13,Fquickly. Within around a minute the
OL,14,Fincident had been assessed and passed
OL,15,Fto officers, who decided they would
OL,16,Fcontact the victim but were unable to
OL,17,Fintercept the train before the
OL,18,Fsuspects got off.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,FThe passenger then replied to us in
OL,8,Fthe contact centre: "It's too late.
OL,9,FThe boys have gone off. I don't need
OL,10,Fany help."
OL,12,FI found myself feeling a bit deflated.
OL,13,FWatching those exchanges unfold in
OL,14,Freal time brought home just how
OL,15,Fquickly opportunities to identify
OL,16,Fsuspects can disappear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,FWe travelled to the British Transport
OL,8,FPolice's CCTV control room near London
OL,9,FVictoria. This is where incidents like
OL,10,Fthe one I'd seen in the text centre
OL,11,Fget sent for further investigations.
OL,13,FThe team has access to around 150,000
OL,14,Fcameras across the railway network,
OL,15,Fwhile footage from trains can also be
OL,16,Frequested from train operators.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,FAs investigators worked through
OL,8,Fappeals and reviewed footage from
OL,9,Fstations across England and Wales, I
OL,10,Fcouldn't help thinking about Esme's
OL,11,Fcase and the CCTV appeal that had once
OL,12,Fbeen put together in an effort to
OL,13,Fidentify the men she reported.
OL,15,FIt is painstaking work, often
OL,16,Finvolving tracking someone's movements
OL,17,Facross multiple stations and piecing
OL,18,Ftogether evidence from different
OL,19,Fcamera systems.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,FLater that day, I joined officers from
OL,8,Fthe new Violence Against Women and
OL,9,FGirls Taskforce for a patrol at
OL,10,FVictoria Station.
OL,12,FThe shift began with a briefing. Maps
OL,13,Fof stations were pinned shown to us on
OL,14,Fa PowerPoint detailing the operations
OL,15,Faims, highlighting CCTV coverage,
OL,16,Fknown hotspots and the locations
OL,17,Fofficers wanted to focus on.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,FSome officers were in BTP uniform.
OL,8,FOthers would blend into the crowds in
OL,9,Fplain clothes, watching for behaviour
OL,10,Fthat might indicate someone was
OL,11,Ftargeting women.
OL,13,FDetective Sergeant Dave Hewison
OL,14,Fexplained they were looking for
OL,15,Fpredatory behaviour rather than
OL,16,Fwaiting for offences to be reported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,FIt was one of the hottest days of the
OL,8,Fyear and as we entered the station you
OL,9,Fcould see the sense of reassurance
OL,10,Fthat uniformed officers give to
OL,11,Fmembers of the public.
OL,13,FThere were groups travelling through
OL,14,Fthe station heading to see Harry
OL,15,FStyles at Wembley. Officers approached
OL,16,Fa man whose behaviour had caught their
OL,17,Fattention.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,FMoments later his girlfriend stepped
OL,8,Foff the train, the pair embraced and
OL,9,Feveryone laughed as officers made a
OL,10,Fheart-shaped gesture towards our
OL,11,Fcamera.
OL,13,FIt turned out to be nothing. "But
OL,14,Fwithout those interventions," Dave
OL,15,Ftold me afterwards, "we wouldn't know
OL,16,Fthat".
OL,18,FIn February 2025, officers boarded a
OL,19,Ftrain to arrest a man after police
OL,20,Freceived a 999 call from a passenger.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,FA man was arrested for outraging
OL,8,Fpublic decency, but also was wanted
OL,9,Ffor rape. He's now in jail because
OL,10,FDorothea, who has waived her right to
OL,11,Fanonymity, reported him staring and
OL,12,Fthen masturbating in front of her and
OL,13,Fher mother on the train.
OL,15,FShe told ITV News women should be
OL,16,Fempowered to report all incidents: "It
OL,17,Fis violating. It's just awful. Even
OL,18,Fthough he didn't come into contact
OL,19,Fwith me and physically touch me or
OL,20,Fharm me.
OL,26,@xD@dOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,F"It's just as offensive. If I hadn't
OL,8,Freported. That's what some people deem
OL,9,Fas a small a crime. He wouldn't have
OL,10,Fgot found for what he did to the other
OL,11,Fvictim. I think about her every single
OL,12,Fday."
OL,14,FKabir Rahamati was convicted of both
OL,15,Foffences and on 24 October 2025 he was
OL,16,Fjailed for nine years, plus eight
OL,17,Fyears on extended licence.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31317
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,FI rejoined the taskforce in
OL,8,FBirmingham, at New Street Station, for
OL,9,Fanother operation. British Transport
OL,10,FPolice tell me that New Street is a
OL,11,Fhotspot for this type of behaviour as
OL,12,Fit's so busy, particularly with people
OL,13,Ftravelling later at night.
OL,15,FWithin minutes of arriving, officers
OL,16,Fmade an arrest under the new offence
OL,17,Fof intentional harassment, alarm or
OL,18,Fdistress on the basis of sex. Officers
OL,19,Ftold me the high-visibility patrols
OL,20,Facted on intelligence from the CCTV
OL,21,Funit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31318
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Nia Mellor,
OL,8,Fwho leads the force's work on violence
OL,9,Fagainst women and girls, told me
OL,10,Fofficers are taking a far more
OL,11,Fproactive approach.
OL,13,F"If you think you can come onto the
OL,14,Frailway and behave like that," she
OL,15,Fsaid, "action will be taken."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31319
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,FAs we continued filming, a woman
OL,8,Fapproached station staff after seeing
OL,9,Fa man with his trousers down. Anti-
OL,10,Fsocial behaviour officers escorted a
OL,11,Fman from the station, although no
OL,12,Farrest was made.
OL,14,FLater that night another report came
OL,15,Fin from a train, and we watched as
OL,16,Fofficers escorted two young women to
OL,17,Fthe taxi bays to get them home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31320
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,FAfter two days with British Transport
OL,8,FPolice taskforce, it was quite clear
OL,9,Fthat officers are prioritising
OL,10,Fpreventing offending against women and
OL,11,Fgirls on the network.
OL,13,FBut for passengers like Esme, it is
OL,14,Ffrustrating to see suspects disappear
OL,15,Finto the crowds.
OL,17,FBritish Transport Police told us:
OL,18,F"Tackling sexual offending on the
OL,19,Frailway is a force priority for us,
OL,20,Fand we're committed to protecting
OL,21,Feveryone's right to a safe journey.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31321
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784663291
OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,F"We're tireless in our efforts to
OL,8,Fraise public awareness of when and how
OL,9,Fto report crime, such as using our
OL,10,Fdiscreet text-to-report service.
OL,12,F"No report is too small or too trivial
OL,13,F` every single sex offence reported to
OL,14,Fus is taken extremely seriously and we
OL,15,Fwill always do everything in our power
OL,16,Fto bring predatory offenders to
OL,17,Fjustice.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
