OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,F"The 61016 number receives over a
OL,8,Fquarter of a million texts every year
OL,9,F` and this figure continues to rise as
OL,10,Fconfidence grows among passengers in
OL,11,Freporting historically underreported
OL,12,Fcrimes, such as sexual offending.
OL,14,F"This confidence isn't misplaced, as
OL,15,Fwe've shown time and time again that
OL,16,Fwe won't stop until we've caught
OL,17,Foffenders, put them before the courts,
OL,18,Fand secured justice for victims."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@aO]
