OL,3,COn patrol with new police taskforce
OL,4,Cstopping sex offenders on Britain's
OL,5,Crailways
OL,7,FFor generations, women have changed
OL,8,Fthe way they travel to try and keep
OL,9,Fthemselves safe. Now the police is
OL,10,Fchanging its approach to tackling the
OL,11,Foffences against women and girls on
OL,12,Fthe transport network.
OL,14,FOfficers are encouraging more women to
OL,15,Freport what happens to them, so that
OL,16,Fmore offenders can be identified.
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G23/24
